{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

[GROUNDING RULES]
- Only reference columns listed above in the dataset section.
- If you are unsure about a pandas function or method, say "정확하지 않을 수 있어요" instead of guessing.
- Do not fabricate any data, column names, or function behavior not confirmed in the context.
